{"tid":1772688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"＜民主，無辦法當飯食＞","createTime":"2019-12-07T00:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T13:28:30.000Z","uid":142242,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"faf30ac961f29ac035fb988db191587e3d78186f","tid":1772688,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:39:18.000Z","msg":"有位台灣朋友share咗一首台語詩，幾有意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">&lt;民主，無法度準飯食&gt;<br />\n<br />\n民主，無法度準飯食<br />\n民主，予咱半暝仔袂驚惶<br />\n會當隨時遊山倚海<br />\n享受山風，海景<br />\n<br />\n民主，無法度準飯食<br />\n民主，予咱3、5个人自由開講<br />\n談天說地，講政治頭人八卦<br />\n<br />\n民主，無法度準飯食<br />\n民主，予咱按司法程序訴訟<br />\n袂無代無誌安咱無影的罪名<br />\n<br />\n民主，無法度準飯食<br />\n民主，予咱會當罵總統<br />\n袂凊采掠咱入反政府的監<br />\n抑是，予人暗殺<br />\n<br />\n民主，無法度準飯食<br />\n偌濟人用伊的汗佮血<br />\n予咱自由自在食飯－－<br />\n佇餐廳食－－毋是集中營<br />\n<br />\n有一工<br />\n咱隨時會失蹤<br />\n袂當自由自在食飯的時<br />\n咱會知影<br />\n民主，比食飯較要緊<br />\n<br />\n2019.04.17 內湖-西湖半伏居<br />\n2019.12.02 ＜台灣教會公報＞3536期</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小弟都識少少台語，試下譯做廣東話：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">&lt;民主，無辦法當飯食&gt;<br />\n<br />\n民主，無辦法當飯食<br />\n民主，畀我哋半夜唔使驚<br />\n可以隨時遊山玩水<br />\n享受山風，海景<br />\n<br />\n民主，無辦法當飯食<br />\n民主，畀我哋3、5個人自由傾偈<br />\n談天說地，講政治元首八卦<br />\n<br />\n民主，無辦法當飯食<br />\n民主，畀我哋按司法程序訴訟<br />\n唔會無事無幹砌我哋生豬肉<br />\n<br />\n民主，無辦法當飯食<br />\n民主，畀我哋可以鬧總統<br />\n唔會隨便拉我哋去坐反政府嘅監<br />\n抑或係，畀人暗殺<br />\n<br />\n民主，無辦法當飯食<br />\n有幾多人用佢哋嘅汗同血<br />\n畀我哋自由自在食飯－－<br />\n喺餐廳食－－唔係集中營<br />\n<br />\n有一日<br />\n我哋隨時會失蹤<br />\n無得自由自在食飯嗰陣<br />\n我哋會知道<br />\n民主，比食飯更加緊要</span>"},{"pid":"d4d0212eaab5e740bcdd0373854efc9da5296b1d","tid":1772688,"uid":2612,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">128 維園見</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tM1AHsT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtM1AHsT.jpg&h=51b9806f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nZ3GC1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnZ3GC1d.jpg&h=a58f11cd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3czX1e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3czX1e.jpg&h=afb0dc00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JMAmC1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJMAmC1f.jpg&h=565489c9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OQkE87V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOQkE87V.jpg&h=ca6df116&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f6a91563bd8ff996c2704dc5b4686daa3796fa0a","tid":1772688,"uid":254183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:08.000Z","msg":"民主唔能當飯食<br />\n冇民主，你只能同統治者乞食"},{"pid":"e1dbe5c3eb622b5fd101a19f1996d5334757c690","tid":1772688,"uid":226421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"因為民主係超越食飯屙屎嘅層次<br />\n當然唔可以當飯食"},{"pid":"adef211a432abee259895ac96f09acd4376ee728","tid":1772688,"uid":142242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6a91563bd8ff996c2704dc5b4686daa3796fa0a","tid":1772688,"uid":254183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:08.000Z","msg":"民主唔能當飯食<br />\n冇民主，你只能同統治者乞食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:42:01.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"1ec3a1e59b533267f8369e9883ec4304df380579","tid":1772688,"uid":142242,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e1dbe5c3eb622b5fd101a19f1996d5334757c690","tid":1772688,"uid":226421,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T00:41:26.000Z","msg":"因為民主係超越食飯屙屎嘅層次<br />\n當然唔可以當飯食"},"citedBy":0,"r